{"number":94,"ayahs":[{"numberInSurah":1,"arabic":" أَلَمْ نَشْرَحْ لَكَ صَدْرَكَ","translation":"Did We not expand for you, [O Muḥammad], your breast?","transliteration":"Alam nashrah laka sadrak","page":596},{"numberInSurah":2,"arabic":"وَوَضَعْنَا عَنكَ وِزْرَكَ","translation":"And We removed from you your burden","transliteration":"WawadaAAna AAanka wizrak","page":596},{"numberInSurah":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِىٓ أَنقَضَ ظَهْرَكَ","translation":"Which had weighed upon your back","transliteration":"Allathee anqada thahrak","page":596},{"numberInSurah":4,"arabic":"وَرَفَعْنَا لَكَ ذِكْرَكَ","translation":"And raised high for you your repute.","transliteration":"WarafaAAna laka thikrak","page":596},{"numberInSurah":5,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ ٱلْعُسْرِ يُسْرًا","translation":"For indeed, with hardship [will be] ease [i.e., relief].","transliteration":"Fa-inna maAAa alAAusri yusra","page":596},{"numberInSurah":6,"arabic":"إِنَّ مَعَ ٱلْعُسْرِ يُسْرًا","translation":"Indeed, with hardship [will be] ease.","transliteration":"Inna maAAa alAAusri yusra","page":596},{"numberInSurah":7,"arabic":"فَإِذَا فَرَغْتَ فَٱنصَبْ","translation":"So when you have finished [your duties], then stand up [for worship].","transliteration":"Fa-itha faraghta fansab","page":596},{"numberInSurah":8,"arabic":"وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَٱرْغَب","translation":"And to your Lord direct [your] longing.","transliteration":"Wa-ila rabbika farghab","page":596}]}